        <h3>Pasadena catering kitchen, Cleveland Range KEL-40 electric (year 9)</h3>
        <p>Kettle not heating at all. Element open circuit on multimeter. Replaced heating element with OEM Cleveland Range part. While there, descaled jacket interior (LA hard water buildup). Tested under load 45 minutes. Total: $120 plus $740 element plus $260 descale plus 120 minutes labor = $1,260.</p>
      </div>
