        <p>Element drawing power but heating slowly. Diagnosed contactor relay with pitted contacts (intermittent connection causing inconsistent power). Replaced contactor. Tested heating cycle to setpoint within spec. Total: $120 plus $440 part plus 60 minutes labor = $600.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

